frames.caption: A powerful superhero figure stands amidst a cityscape engulfed in flames and destruction. The character is poised with energy emanating from their hands, set against a dramatic red and orange sky. Skyscrapers in the background are partially destroyed, adding to the apocalyptic atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a superhero in a futuristic, dystopian city setting. The character is central to the image, exuding power and energy in a moment of intense action. The environment is chaotic, with fire and destruction dominating the landscape.

frames.caption: A futuristic warrior stands amidst a city in ruins, with a fiery sky overhead. The figure is clad in glowing armor, emanating energy from their hands. Skyscrapers crumble around them, accentuating the chaos of the scene.
frames.description: The scene depicts a post-apocalyptic cityscape with a central figure in advanced armor. The environment is chaotic, with buildings collapsing and a dramatic, fiery sky creating a sense of impending doom.
